{"tid":1890442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再生障礙症貧血少女　急需屍肺移植　醫生：唔做係死梗","createTime":"2020-02-21T08:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T12:23:17.000Z","uid":9846,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6e8d7b528e989dd0253060785718e926e0d9fe","tid":1890442,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:00:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/再生障礙症貧血-24-歲女求-o-血型雙葉屍肺-醫生-唔做移植係死梗/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%86%8D%E7%94%9F%E9%9A%9C%E7%A4%99%E7%97%87%E8%B2%A7%E8%A1%80-24-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E6%B1%82-o-%E8%A1%80%E5%9E%8B%E9%9B%99%E8%91%89%E5%B1%8D%E8%82%BA-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%94%94%E5%81%9A%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D%E4%BF%82%E6%AD%BB%E6%A2%97%2F&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=b6d133a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E5%86%8D%E7%94%9F%E9%9A%9C%E7%A4%99%E7%97%87%E8%B2%A7%E8%A1%80-24-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E6%B1%82-o-%E8%A1%80%E5%9E%8B%E9%9B%99%E8%91%89%E5%B1%8D%E8%82%BA-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%94%94%E5%81%9A%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D%E4%BF%82%E6%AD%BB%E6%A2%97%2F&h=bcbe16c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/再生障礙症貧血-24-歲女求-o-血型雙葉屍肺-醫生-唔做移植係死梗/</a><br />\n<br />\n24歲女子吳犖晴自初中患有再生障礙症貧血，要經常輸血補充身體匱乏的紅血球、白血球及血小板。至去年末接受骨髓移植後，身體繼而出現併發症，肺部小靜脈阻塞，功能喪失，不能維持血液循環。她正在醫院深切治療部以體外人工心肺機維持生命，其母親表示犖晴願望是「做個普通人，去吓旅行」，急需換肺續命。院方形容肺部移植是「犖晴的唯一希望」，呼籲有心人捐出 O 血型的雙葉屍肺。"},{"pid":"07247db53343f450bf83a2783aeb8dacee24047f","tid":1890442,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"23bda4c41d7725af6656c15a13f01f7719a0cbd2","tid":1890442,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72446530e0a12fa5ca495806905971754cf729e2","tid":1890442,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:05:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已